text: Mansour Hazrati (born 14 April 1932) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman middleweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tehran
